## 1. License and Scope of Use
Ceibo Apps grants you a personal, non-exclusive, non-transferable, and limited license to use the App for personal, non-commercial purposes on a compatible device.

## 2. Local Operation & No Data Collection
As described in our **Privacy Policy**, Ceibo Apps apps operate locally on your device.

* **Permissions:** Any device permissions requested by an App (such as audio, camera, or storage access) are used solely to provide the App’s core functionality. No data accessed through these permissions is collected, stored, or transmitted by Ceibo Apps.
* **No Accounts:** Ceibo Apps apps do not require user accounts, except where required by the Google Play Store for distribution or purchases.
* **Third-Party Content:** Some apps may provide access to content or services operated by third parties (such as radio streams). Ceibo Apps does not own, control, or guarantee the availability, accuracy, legality, or continuity of third-party content.

